Pendulum Effect
 You cannot Pendulum Summon monsters, except "Nekroz" or "Sephira" monsters. This effect cannot be negated.

 Monster Effect
 If a "Nekroz" or "Sephira" card(s) in your Monster Zone or Pendulum Zone is destroyed by battle or card effect, except "Sephira Exa the Flame Beast Nekroz", while this card is in your hand or Graveyard: You can Special Summon this card. You can only use this effect of "Sephira Exa the Flame Beast Nekroz" once per turn.
